          h2 Instructions
          ul
            li #[a(href="https://www.google.com/search?q=turn+off+enhance+pointer+precision" target="blank") Make sure that "Enhance pointer precision" is off].
            li Update the #[i in-game sensitivity] to your preference.            
            li Pick a weapon, mag size, and attachments' level.
            li Click anywhere on the area below.
            li Get a high score by compensating a recoil.
          p Default (6/11) Windows Mouse Sensitivity is assumed.
          p Enable #[i Show path] to see the ideal compensation trajectory.
          p Enable #[i Show pacer] to see a running dot to follow (works only if "Show path" is on).
          p #[i Auto toggle hint] switches "show path" between sprays.
          p The #[i middle mouse button] toggles the display mode of a trace.
          p I recommend "Show path", "Show pacer" and "Auto toggle hint" enabled to learn the patterns.
